Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw a beast rising out of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,having ten horns and seven heads;\Nand on its horns were ten diadems,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and on its heads were blasphemous names…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They worshipped the dragon, for he had\Ngiven his authority to the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and they worshipped the beast, saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is like the beast,\Nand who can fight against it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Revelation 13:1-4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was amazing.\N-You were great as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was such a difficult brain aneurysm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but you did the clipping so speedily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an excellent surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could once again witness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the genius of Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't have done it\Nwithout everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's so late in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was a six-hour surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any outpatients today.\NGet some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,1986, DÜSSELDORF (GERMANY)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,KENZO TENMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't how it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,EVA HEINEMANN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one being woken\Nwith kisses like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eva. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now in Düsseldorf. Mr. Lyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo, did you forget about our date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert, an adviser in the East German\NTrade Bureau, has arrived to seek asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He appeared in front of the reporters\Nwith his family yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Liebert appeared to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Their son and daughter,\Na pair of fraternal twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,looked happy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be staying in Düsseldorf\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The government will be taking care\Nof their well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel rested…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wake up! It's your news!\N-…the opera singer Mr. Rosenbach
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was in a critical condition\Ndue to a hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He is now in a stable condition\Nfollowing surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation was\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, the hospital's director\NDr. Heinemann held a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosenbach was diagnosed\Nwith a ruptured brain aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery went smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the clipping was very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us his chance of recovery\Nas he has many fans waiting for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We will give it our best to help him\Nget his voice back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Heinemann's team has performed\Nnumerous complex surgeries in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This surgery has certainly confirmed\Nour country's status
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the medical community.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about me.\NIt's news about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all because you did\Nthe perfect surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as one of father's team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he appreciates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one getting the hospital\Nsuch great recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of your father
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can work in Germany like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be okay if you just\Nfollow father's lead and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nhe becomes board chairman at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will soon be Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll be the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the Director's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not built for a hard life,\Nso you'd better make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out or…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 128/64.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain spatula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to trim the medullary pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, your surgery\Nwas excellent as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,DR. BECKER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And surgery isn't\Nthe only thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Being Head of Neurosurgery at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director and Chief of Surgery\Nboth favor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You even have the heart\Nof the Director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say, Dr. Becker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't mean anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that it's all politics\Nin the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you know that the Director\Nis just using you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked about the opera singer's surgery\Nas if he was the one who operated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,during the televised press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being used is proof\Nthat you have the skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're promoted,\Ndon't forget about me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a drink some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my husband back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do his surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband was brought into the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before that opera singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you put off his operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the best doctor\Nin this hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to perform the surgery\Non the Turkish construction worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Operation Room One immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director's order. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did his surgery,\Nhe might have lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,…and I was fighting over\Nthat dress with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only dress of that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, are you listening?\N-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker did the surgery\Non that Turkish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He obviously took too long\Nto perform the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did the surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that Turkish man could have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. We're having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what did she want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the Director's order
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the opera singer's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Npeople's lives aren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the neighbor called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How many gunshots?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,About five to six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who lives in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's… where the East German defector\NMr. Liebert has been staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This could be problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On my count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a survivor! It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and a woman are dead,\Nand a boy is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat, a boy is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the boy the only patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Both of his parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it was a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will be at the hospital\Nin five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Heinemann, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to have kept your daughter out\Nso late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Eva's fiancé,\Nso don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come in for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you told your parents in Japan\Nabout the wedding date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But my father is a doctor\Nat a small private practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know if he would have\Ntime to come to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a good chance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for him to come\Nand enjoy a bit of traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It'd be our pleasure to have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful to you\Nfor taking me under your wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came to Germany,\NI thought you were like a high school boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're the up-and-coming\Ntop surgeon at Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kenzo, about your research
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on cerebral vasospasm following\Nsubarachnoid hemorrhage…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm making a model of a dog\Nwith subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're canceling\Nthe research project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be a presenter\Nat the next symposium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the European Society\Nfor Emergency Medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to prepare my speech draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am almost done with my research--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a tough afternoon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some shady NGO came to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and protested about the surgery\Nfor the opera singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that we put off\Nthe Turkish man's surgery for the singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Turkish man's surgery\Nwas performed earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with our procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they think doctors\Nare volunteers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to advance as academic scholars\Nbefore we can save lives. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you for my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes… Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-How is the patient?\N-He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How are his vitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 72/50.\NPulse rate is 137.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet entered from his forehead…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the X-rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the boy's twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Any injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but she has suffered\Nsevere mental trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The X-rays and CT scans\Nof his head are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It entered deep into the brain\Nfrom his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet grazed\Nhis left middle cerebral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we moved the bullet even a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the artery might break\Nand lead to hemorrhaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be late\Nwhen you're the one on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do a bifrontal craniotomy,\Nclean up any bones and infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we will carefully\Ntake the bullet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we will do angioplasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take some time,\Nbut let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 120/80\Nand pulse rate is 92. Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anesthetic applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dr. Tenma.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Operating Room One right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor Roedecker has collapsed\Nwith cerebral thrombus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He will arrive in ten minutes\Nby helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please call Dr. Boyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have an arterial occlusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nyou will do the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm about to start\Non the surgery for that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving you to take care of the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Dr. Eisen and Dr. Boyer coming
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm just getting ready\Nfor another surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let Dr. Becker handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you,\Nmy current patient's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,left middle cerebral artery\Nwas grazed by a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a very complicated surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer can operate on the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be the one\Nto operate on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, just do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and save the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has promised that\Nhe will increase
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our hospital's subsidy\Nduring the next medical audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Tenma.\NI have high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has arrived at the heliport!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do an angiogram after the CT scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Check where the thrombotic occlusion is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're relying on your genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they think doctors\Nare volunteers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to advance as academic scholars\Nbefore we can save lives. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the Director's order
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the opera singer's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Npeople's lives aren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did his surgery,\Nhe might have lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another surgery to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor is having a CT scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the CT scan room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Hold on. I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
